<plot>Melodramatic treatment of "love in the time of war". Two soldiers, friends, return to Athens from the Albanian front. They meet a girl whom one of them had known and corresponded with some time ago. Things get complicated as the girl shows interest in the second soldier, and thus a fateful rift between the two friends occurs. In the end, the good friend discreetly backs off, and the situation is resolved.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?025628</url></doc>
